org.codice.ddf.registry.federationadmin.internal

Interface FederationAdminMBean

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FederationAdmin

    public interface FederationAdminMBean
    This is the external facing interface for the FederationAdminService. This is what should be used by the UI, for example, to interact with the FederationAdminService.

    • Method Detail

      • createLocalEntry

        String createLocalEntry(Map<String,Object> registryObjectMap)
                 throws FederationAdminException
        Create a local entry in the registry catalog for the given object map. The map will be converted to a RegistryPackageType using the RegistryPackageWebConverter. The resulting RegistryPackageType will be passed to FederationAdminService#addLocalEntry to create the entry.
        Parameters:
        RegistryObjectMap - A map of the registry object to create
        Returns:
        Id of the created metacard.
        Throws:
        FederationAdminException - Passes exception thrown by FederationAdminServiceImpl

      • createLocalEntry

        String createLocalEntry(String base64EncodedXmlString)
                 throws FederationAdminException
        Create a local entry in the registry catalog for the given string. The String provided is an Base64 encoded representation of a registry package xml. The RegistryTransformer transforms the Base64 decode stream into a registry metacard.
        Parameters:
        base64EncodedXmlString - Base64 encoded registry package xml.
        Returns:
        Id of the created metacard
        Throws:
        FederationAdminException - If Base64 decoding of the string fails If the RegistryTransformer can't convert the stream into a metacard Passes exceptions thrown by FederationAdminServiceImpl

      • updateLocalEntry

        void updateLocalEntry(Map<String,Object> registryObjectMap)
               throws FederationAdminException
        Update a local entry in the registry catalog for the given object map. The map will be converted to a RegistryPackageType using the RegistryPackageWebConverter. The resulting RegistryPackageType will be passed to FederationAdminService#addLocalEntry to update the entry.
        Parameters:
        registryObjectMap - A map of the registry object to update
        Throws:
        FederationAdminException - Passes exception thrown byFederationAdminServiceImpl

      • deleteLocalEntry

        void deleteLocalEntry(List<String> ids)
               throws FederationAdminException
        Deletes a local entry in the registry catalog for each of the ids provided.
        Parameters:
        ids - List of registry ids to be deleted
        Throws:
        FederationAdminException - Passes exception thrown byFederationAdminServiceImpl

      • getLocalNodes

        Map<String,Object> getLocalNodes()
                          throws FederationAdminException
        Returns a Map of RegistryPackageType objects as converted using RegistryPackageWebConverter List of node maps representing local registry entries can be found in the returned map using the key 'nodes'. Additional information about the nodes/registry is also included in the map.
        Returns:
        Map
        Throws:
        FederationAdminException - Passes exception thrown byFederationAdminServiceImpl

      • registryStatus

        boolean registryStatus(String servicePID)
        Parameters:
        servicePID - - The PID of the registry which will have the status checked
        Returns:
        the status of a single registry as a boolean, true if available, false otherwise
